                    <h4 class="text-white">Way of the Water Buffalo</h4>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white">
                        Fag el-Gamous - which means Way of the Water Buffalo - is a large and important cemetery in Egypt that has been under archeological investigation (primarily by BYU researchers)
                        for over 25 years.
                    </p><br />
                    <p class="mb-0 text-white">
                        The excavation has garnered international attention because of the interesting insights gained by studying the Fag el-Gamous mummies.
                    </p>
